Product description

Guajolote Prints Funny Novelty Memo Pads Bundle (4 Items) I Have No Idea What I'm Doing, Everything is Fine, This is my life now, and I'm not even trying anymore. Remind yourself that everything will be OK regardless of worries with these nice paper notepads from Guajolote Prints.

Each paper notepad is 4.25 inches wide by 5.5 inches tall, has 50 sheets of printed paper, it's glued on top, and has a chip board backing for added durability.

Made by Guajolote Prints.
